In order to compile you need GNU make and "ocaml" must be in our PATH.

Compilation under Unix
----------------------

You need the package "libbluetooth2-dev" (under Debian) or equivalent.


Compilation under Windows
-------------------------

If the LEGO® fantom drivers are not installed:

make -f Makefile.win


Compilation under Mac OS X
--------------------------

make -f Makefile.macos
